  <div class="content">
    <p>This calendar features a complete listing of all lessons, practices, workshops, and special events in the RPI Ballroom community, including Argentine Tango, Ballroom/Latin, Lindy Hop Swing, and the Ballroom Team.</p>
<p>If you would like to explore the various dance opportunities in the Albany Capital Region, visit <a href="http://www.ballroomdances.org/dcall.shtml">ballroomdances.org's NY Capital District's Event Calendar</a>, <a href="http://capitalusadance.com/cgi-bin/mods/calendar/index.cgi?vsSD=1">USA Capital Dance's Event Calendar</a>, and <a href="http://www.albanyswingdancing.com/events/index.php">Albany Swing Dancing's Event Calendar</a>.</p>
